the on-demand <%= vars.product_full %> service.

The on-demand service consists of dedicated VMs that serve a single service instance.
The BOSH Director creates each VM on-demand when an app developer creates a service instance.
For more information, see [Unlocking the Power of On-Demand VMware Tanzu RabbitMQ for VMs](./ondemand.html).

